        <item>
        <title>关于 linsk27</title>
        <link>https://linsk27-github-io.vercel.app/about/</link>
        <pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://linsk27-github-io.vercel.app/about/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://linsk27-github-io.vercel.app/img/projects/dev-cockpit-local-development-dashboard.png" alt="Featured image of post 关于 linsk27" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;我是 linsk27，主要把前端、全栈和 AI 辅助开发相关想法做成可以运行、可以验证、可以继续迭代的项目。我的 GitHub 主页是 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/linsk27&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
